These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, cabbage
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, cycling
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person eating cabbage##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | cabbage   | onion  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, peach
2 different pets are kept: snake, horse
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the snake is not the person eating peach##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | plum | peach      |
| Pet    | snake  | horse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
